description:
Monday September 22, 2008

Dave Ramsey offers life-changing financial advice as host of the nationally syndicated radio program, "The Dave Ramsey Show," which is heard by nearly 3 million listeners each week on more than 350 radio stations throughout the United States. The 3-hour live radio talk show focuses on life, love, and relationships, and how they happen to revolve around money.
